 animal owners to follow the law on disposing of fallen stock. </p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong>National Fallen Stock Scheme helpline</strong>  <br />\n0845 054 8888</p>\n</div>\n\n"}]},"updated_at":"2012-10-22T15:26:22+00:00","tags":[{"title":"Business Link","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/businesslink.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":null,"short_description":null,"type":"legacy_source"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=businesslink","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/businesslink"},"parent":null},{"title":"Farming","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/business%2Ffarming.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Health and safety, registering and licensing animals, compliance tools","short_description":null,"type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=business%2Ffarming","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/business/farming"},"parent":{"title":"Businesses and self-employed","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/business.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Information about starting up and running a business in the UK, including help if you're self employed or a sole trader.","short_description":null,"type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=business","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/business"},"parent":null}}],"related":[{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/horse-passport.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/horse-passport","title":"Getting and using a horse passport","format":"guide","details":{"need_id":"1848","business_proposition":false,"description":"Horses, ponies and donkeys must have a horse passport and you must have it with you at all times when you're with your horse\r\n"},"updated_at":"2012-10-22T15:25:22+00:00"}]},{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/single-payment-scheme-online.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/single-payment-scheme-online","title":"Manage your Single Payment Scheme online","format":"transact